Name: Riccioli Salt Baked Fish
AttributesDescription: Increases all team members' DEF by 35% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: The finest ingredients often require only the simplest preparation. Fresh fish, lightly cleaned and baked in sea salt, brings out its pure, natural flavors. For seasoned sailors, this dish is a commonplace staple. However, for the sheltered nobles of Ragunna, it represents their most vivid imagination of the sea.
